data.description: Call The George Shea Team (813) 541-2390 ~ Fishhawk West’s Central Park! Overlooking a Premium / Highly sought after Green Space. Boasting just under 3400sqft with 6 bedrooms and 4 Baths! Steps away from the Community's One of a Kind - LAKE HOUSE, Resort Style Parks and Pool! Check out this Contemporary, Energy Efficient, Amazing Home! Lightly Lived In and Very WELL APPOINTED! Step inside and notice upgrades like Gorgeous Flooring, Double Pane Windows and MORE! You will adore this Plan! The kitchen boasts the latest in designer trends, mosaic tile backsplash, lots of cabinets, granite countertops, backsplash, complete with a stainless steel appliance package. You will find generously sized bedrooms throughout this home. Other special features include a screened / covered patio lanai! This is Truly, A Must See- walking distances from Top Rated Barrington middle and Stowers Elementary schools. This home is an Energy Efficient Home w/ radiant barrier, double pane windows, tankless hot water & More!! Live like you are on Vacation Everyday! Fishhawk Award Winning/Resort Amenities include; Guest Parking, Fitness, Pool, Central Park and the Lake House with pool tables, ping pong, fire pit and More! Minutes to Tampa, MacDill AFB, Golf, World Class/Sugar Sand Beaches, Golf Courses & All that Florida has to Offer! Click on the HD Virtual Tour for Additional Photos and See this Today!

georgesheateam@hotmail.com /813.541.2390
 Ranch is a growing community located in beautiful Southeast Hillsborough County in Lithia, Florida...The community has easy access to roads, schools, shopping, and entertainment. This amazing community is the ideal place to call home. The Fishhawk community offers new and re-sale homes with a contemporary Southern style. Beautiful lawns and gardens outline the wonderful architecture that comprises this amazing community. In addition, this community gives so much back and provides a terrific atmosphere for families. Homeowners of Fishhawk Ranch enjoy an abundant array of community entertainment and involvement. The incredible list of features include a Clubhouse, Central Park Pool, Dog Park, Fully Equipped Fitness Center, the Lake House and over 30 miles of trails.  The community offers two on-site Preschool, The Goddard School for Early Childhood Development and Kids R Kids of Valrico/Circa Fishhawk, with year-round care including before and after school programs. With so much to offer, this is the ideal community for anyone of any age!
